# FOOshi - Restaurant App UI

A responsive restaurant app interface prototype built with pure HTML and CSS. This project demonstrates modern UI design principles and CSS animations without any JavaScript.

## Features

### Layout
- iPhone 16-style transparent mockup frame
- Responsive grid layout for food items
- Custom scrollable content area with hidden scrollbar
- Bottom navigation bar with interactive elements

### UI Components
- Dynamic search bar with expand animation on hover
- Category filter tags (Ramen, Sushi, Rolls) with hover effects
- Hero section with gradient background
- Food item cards with hover animations
- Navigation bar with icon animations

### Design Elements
- Custom SVG icons for status bar
- Linear gradient backgrounds
- Custom button animations
- Smooth hover transitions
- Shadow effects for depth

### Visual Elements
- Status bar with time and system icons
- Expandable search functionality
- Category filter capsules
- Food item grid with images
- Bottom navigation with notification, cart, home, orders, and settings icons

## Technical Details
- Built with semantic HTML5
- Pure CSS3 with modern features:
  - CSS Grid
  - Flexbox
  - Custom Properties (variables)
  - Transform animations
  - Linear gradients
  - Box shadows
  - Border radius
  - Transitions

